      <description>&lt;p&gt;I am involved in MARVIC, an EU SOIL MISSION project developing a &lt;strong&gt;framework for the design of harmonized, context-specific MRV systems for carbon removals by agricultural activities&lt;/strong&gt;. In this project, my research focuses on the &lt;strong&gt;climate benefit of carbon farming solutions&lt;/strong&gt;. I compute the &lt;strong&gt;radiative forcing&lt;/strong&gt; of various carbon farming practices, with the aim of accounting for &lt;strong&gt;possible non-permanency of carbon sequestration and trade-offs between greenhouse gas&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
